				\begin{document}$$\alpha_{a} = \alpha_{ao} {\text{exp }}\left( {E_{ph} /E_{u} } \right) \to E_{u} = \, \delta E_{ph} /\delta (ln(\alpha_{a} ))$$\end{document}where αao is the band tail parameter that can be given by80:3αao=(4πσo/xΔEc)1/2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
